<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Subscription Expired</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #ef4444;">Subscription Expired</h1>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>Your <strong>{{planName}}</strong> subscription for <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> has expired.</p>
  <p>Your business listing has been deactivated and is no longer visible to the public. To reactivate your listing, please renew your subscription.</p>
  <p>
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #ef4444; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
      Renew Subscription
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Digital Directory Team</p>
</body>
</html>
